    • Method Detail

      • main

        public static void main​(String[] args)
        Main function to provide console interface of the program.

        Allowed signature: [-jar] token outputPath

        When -jar is omitted, the program runs in Implementation mode and Impler.implement(Class, Path) is invoked.

        When -jar is used, the program runs in JarImplementation mode and JarImpler.implementJar(Class, Path) is invoked.

        All arguments must not be null. Errors are printed to STDERR.

        Parameters:
        args - Provided to program arguments
